The complications of <COREF ID="6" TYPE="IDENT">Diabetes II</COREF> , such as coronary heart disease , cerebrovascular disease , nephropathy , blindness and lower extremities necrosis , etc. , have become the mankind 's third biggest killer next to cancer and AIDS .
At present , there are more than 20 million diabetics in <COREF ID="12" TYPE="IDENT">China</COREF> which , after <COREF ID="11" TYPE="IDENT">the US</COREF> , is second highest in <COREF ID="10" TYPE="IDENT">the world</COREF> .
