There are no specific statistics on <COREF ID="13" TYPE="IDENT">it</COREF> in <COREF ID="12" TYPE="IDENT">China</COREF> , but <COREF ID="13" TYPE="IDENT">the number of Chinese diabetics</COREF> is increasing by 750,000 annually .
