" <COREF ID="2" TYPE="IDENT">Tang Maikang</COREF> " granules are able to reduce not only blood sugar , but also cholesterol and triglycerides remarkably , and has special curative effects on <COREF ID="1" TYPE="IDENT">the complications of diabetes</COREF> .
